[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說大愛道般泥洹經",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867a21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西晉河內沙門白法祖譯",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867a23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聞如是：一時，佛在墮舍利國，行在獼猴水",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867a24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拘羅曷講堂。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867a25_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時，摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌，行在墮舍利國，與五百比丘尼俱，皆是阿羅漢，皆為大神足，為諄那須、摩訶離、惟讖彌、優波羅洹、卑耶俱曇彌，是輩長年比丘尼大弟子，行在墮舍利王國比丘尼精舍。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867a29_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌，自意覺念言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b01_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我不忍見佛般泥洹，并阿難、舍利弗、目揵連是賢者輩，我先捨壽命行取泥洹去。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時佛即已覺知，便語阿難：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是間摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌自念言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b04_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我不忍見佛般泥洹，并阿難、舍利弗、目乾連是賢者輩，我先捨壽行取泥洹去。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b06_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』是五百比丘尼，自意覺捨一切苦，我不忍見佛般泥洹，并賢者阿難、舍利弗、目乾連是賢者輩，我輩亦當捨壽行取泥洹去。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛說如是。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b09_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿難白佛言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是故我身不能自勝，諸方不能分別，所聞法不能自識。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b11_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聞摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌當般泥洹。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b12_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛便告賢者阿難：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b12_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是阿難！",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b12_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝自意念：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b13_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌，持精進種般泥洹耶，并定種、慈種、解種、度知見種所法，我自知證覺者，若四意止、若四意斷、若四神足、若五根、若五力、七覺意、若八慧道行，汝恐摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌，持是法去耶？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b17_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛說是竟已，阿難白言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌，終不能持清淨種般泥洹去，亦不能持定種，亦不能持慧種，亦不能持解種，亦不能持慧見知種，終不能持覺種。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b21_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛自慧所覺知法，若四意止、若四意斷、若四神足、若五根、若五力、若七覺意，若八慧道行，終不能持是法般泥洹。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b23_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿難言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我自念摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌於佛有阜恩，佛母壽終時，摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌乳養長大佛。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「阿難！",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b26_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有是。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b26_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌，於我有阜恩，我母壽終時乳養長大我。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b27_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「阿難！",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b28_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我亦於摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌有恩無量。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b29_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867b29_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌從我因緣，自歸佛，自歸法，自歸比丘僧，自歸習道盡，亦不復疑佛，亦不復疑法，亦不復疑比丘僧，亦不復疑習道盡，皆已了知。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c03_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人，阿難！",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "能教人自歸佛者、自歸法者、自歸比丘僧者，自歸習道盡者，受者盡壽命者，遷事所受歸教，施與衣食臥具醫藥，所索不逆，盡壽命如是，尚未能為報師恩。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c07_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c07_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是故阿難！",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我於摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌，有阜恩無量。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌，并五百比丘尼，便俱出墮舍利國到大樹間，至佛所以頭面禮佛足却住一處，是五百比丘尼亦復禮佛住一處。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌便叉手白佛言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我不能忍見佛般泥洹，并阿難、舍利弗羅、目乾連是賢者輩比丘，我欲先捨壽行取泥洹去。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」以白如是，佛受摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌所白默然。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c16_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌便以手摩佛足言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今日最後見世間依者，最後見世間明者，最後見世間無上者，從今以後不復見三界中尊者。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c19_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」已為佛作禮却坐一處。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c19_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是五百比丘尼亦復叉手，白佛如是：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c20_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我輩不忍見佛般泥洹，并賢者阿難、舍利弗羅、目乾連賢者比丘輩，我輩欲捨壽行取泥洹去。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c22_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」五百比丘尼白如是，佛默然受五百比丘尼所白。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c23_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五百比丘尼便頭面禮佛足言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c24_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我輩最後見世間依者，最後見世間明者，最後見世間無上者，從今以後不復見三界中尊者。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c26_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」已說如是各還就座。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0867c27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛為摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌并五百比丘尼，說若干品法已訖，皆歡喜起坐，皆為佛作禮繞佛三匝，頭面著地還到墮舍利國，入王園比丘尼精舍，便從一處布五百座，摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌，并五百比丘尼各就座。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868a03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌，便自現神足從坐中沒身去，從東方出，在虛空中，上一樹間上至七樹間，自現四神足，於虛空上經行；",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868a06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "已經行便住，已住便坐，已坐便臥，已臥便自身出五色火，上身出五色火，下身出水，下身出五色火，上身出水；",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868a08_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是從東方沒出西方，從南方沒出北方，便從七樹間下至地變化現神足如於上，時便滅神足取泥洹去。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868a10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時五百比丘尼便皆於坐中沒身，從東方出，在虛空中，上一樹間上至七樹間，自現四品神足，於虛空中經行；",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868a13_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "已經行便住，已住便坐，已坐便臥，已臥便自身出五色火，上身出五色火，下身出水，下身出五色火，上身出水；",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868a15_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是從東方沒出西方，從南方沒出北方，便從七樹間下至地，變化現神足如於上，時便滅神足取泥洹去。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868a18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時，佛告賢者阿難：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868a19_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝行明日平旦入惟舍利國到耶陀迦羅越舍，已到便告耶陀迦羅越，佛母般泥洹，并五百比丘尼，佛勸令迦羅越作五百輿床、五百瓶麻油、五百分香、五百分薪，若干種花香、若干種伎樂，持到王園比丘尼精舍。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868a24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868a24_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛母般泥洹并五百比丘尼，皆是阿羅漢皆大神足，功德已滿，當好葬之。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868a26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛語阿難：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868a26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「告迦羅越，佛勸如是。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868a26_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿難聞佛言，唯然即起持頭面禮佛足，即以平旦入惟舍利國，至耶陀迦羅越所，至已告守門者：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868a28_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「令入白迦羅越，阿難在外。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868a29_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」守門者聞阿難言，即入白如是。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時耶陀迦羅越在高樓上，與妓女共相娛樂，聞門者言如是，即恐怖衣毛皆竪，即下樓出與阿難相見，即持頭面著賢者阿難足下為禮，白賢者阿難：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b04_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是非恒亦非小事。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b04_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b05_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "賢者來入國一何早耶？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b05_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」耶陀迦羅越言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「已意何？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b06_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿難即報言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b06_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「佛使我來，欲勸令迦羅越，作五百輿床、五百麻油瓶、五百分香、五百分薪，若干種好香花、若干種伎樂，持到王園比丘尼精舍。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b09_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b09_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛母般泥洹并五百比丘尼，皆是阿羅漢皆大神足，功德已滿，當好葬之。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b11_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛勸迦羅越如是。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b11_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦羅越聞阿難言如是，即惛擗地言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b12_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「賢者阿難！",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我人有何等過於比丘尼？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b13_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘尼有何恨我人？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b13_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所般泥洹不告我人？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "賢者阿難！",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b14_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從今以後，行室當空，諸座亦當空，經行處亦當空，四徼道頭里巷皆當空，惟舍利國已為空。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "賢者阿難！",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b16_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從今以後，不復見比丘尼行分越入惟舍利國，是痛何甚！",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」耶陀迦羅越言已竟，阿難即告迦羅越言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「佛本自說言，一切恩愛皆當別離消散，各自異處各自異行，所生所至所想，各自有行，各自有因緣，會當滅盡會當別離，欲令不別離者終不可得，慧人但當護法行。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b22_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時賢者阿難，為迦羅越引若干經，要持解迦羅越意，欲勸迦羅越意，已解已喜已勸，便到惟舍利國。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "披羅門迦羅越異因緣，在講堂聚會，便賢者阿難，以到就座已坐，便告惟舍利國披羅門迦羅越：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b27_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「卿輩作五百輿床、五百麻油瓶、五百分香、五百分薪，若干種好香華、若干種妓樂，持到王園比丘尼精舍。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b29_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868b29_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛母般泥洹并五百比丘尼，皆是阿羅漢皆大神足，功德已滿，當好葬之。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c02_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛勸眾披羅門迦羅越如是。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」惟舍利國披羅門迦羅越，即便擗地告賢者阿難：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c04_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我人有何等過於比丘尼？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘尼有何恨我人輩？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "持何等失比丘尼意，般泥洹不告我人？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "賢者阿難！",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c06_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從今以後，行室皆當空，諸座皆當空，四徼道頭里巷皆當空，惟舍利國以為空。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c08_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從今以後，終不復見比丘尼入惟舍利國行分越。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c09_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時，賢者阿難告惟舍利國披羅門迦羅越：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c10_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「佛先自說，一切恩愛皆當別離消散，各自異處各自異行，所生所至所想，各自有行，各自有因緣，會當別離，欲令不別離終不可得，慧人但當護法行。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c13_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時，賢者阿難，為惟舍利國披羅門迦羅越，引若干經要持解披羅門迦羅越意，喜披羅門迦羅越意，勸披羅門迦羅越意，已解已喜已勸，賢者阿難，便起坐到佛所。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時耶陀迦羅越，并五百披羅門迦羅越，持五百輿床、五百麻油瓶、五百分薪、五百分香，若干種好香華妓樂，到王園比丘尼精舍，已到是時王園比丘尼精舍門閉，耶陀迦羅越便告一人言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c21_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「來，汝上一人肩上，度垣牆入園開門。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是人受迦羅越言，上一人肩上度垣牆即開門。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c23_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "耶游陀迦羅越及五百披羅門，俱入王園比丘尼精舍。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c24_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時五百比丘尼共有六沙彌利，是六沙彌利告耶游陀迦羅越言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「賢者迦羅越！",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c26_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "莫得嬈是五百比丘尼也。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c27_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "皆是已得定意坐者。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時，迦羅越告六沙彌利言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c28_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是五百比丘尼，不為定意生，已捨壽命行取泥洹。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0868c29_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時，六沙彌利聞是語即惛擗地言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a01_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「誰當復教誡我人者耶？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a02_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "誰當復諫數我人，當持衣鉢隨誰後耶？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時，迦羅越告賢者六沙彌利言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a03_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「佛先自說，一切恩愛皆當別離。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "賢者沙彌利莫愁憂，但當勤行增精進。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a05_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時，迦羅越取摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌舍利，持若干種香花妓樂，恭敬撿取舍利著金床上，并五百比丘尼舍利亦如是，便耶游陀迦羅越，并五百披羅門迦羅越，俱取摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌，并五百比丘尼舍利到佛所。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時，佛告賢者舍利弗羅：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝來！",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "正東向叉手，下右膝著地，說如是：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a11_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『有在東方直信者直業者，三神六智大神足功德已滿者，皆來到是間。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a13_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a13_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛母般泥洹并五百比丘尼已般泥洹，皆是阿羅漢皆大神足，功德已滿，當共好葬之。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a15_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』南方亦爾西方亦爾，北方亦爾，東方亦爾。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a16_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」賢者舍利弗羅受語，即東向、南向、西向、北向請諸阿羅漢。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a17_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即時東方有三百五十阿羅漢來，南方亦爾，西方亦爾，北方亦爾，合千阿羅漢在佛前。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a19_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛便與千比丘僧俱，到摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌舍利所，佛便坐，千比丘皆就座。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時，佛便告賢者阿難：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝起，取摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌舍利，以鉢盛之，持來著我手中。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a23_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿難言：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a23_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唯然。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」便起坐取摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌舍利，著鉢中持授佛，佛即以兩手受之。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a25_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌舍利已受，佛便告眾比丘僧：",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869a26_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是母人聚舍利也，本是惡身急弊卒暴輕心數轉嫉妬，摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌，已捨母人聚身，男子所應得者摩訶卑耶和題為已得也。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869b01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時佛令耶游陀迦羅越眾比丘僧，共為摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌并五百比丘尼起塔，已起塔及惟舍利國人民及諸天人，皆共事摩訶卑耶和題俱曇彌并五百比丘尼塔。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869b05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說如是，諸比丘皆歡喜，起前為佛作禮而去。",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869b06_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說大愛道般泥洹經",
        "from": "T02n0144_001:0869b07_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]